{"tid":129439,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對川普的看法？ 北韓民眾：沒興趣了解美國事務","createTime":"2017-02-21T14:54:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T16:18:45.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7dbc35a7d3341d5cccd407912b2d95825b3b63b4","tid":129439,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T14:54:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1981819\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1981819&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRqNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=7b5142d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1981819&h=14b3cb6f\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1981819</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國總統川普自大選以來，在全球引起諸多的關注與話題，不過，美國媒體CNN走訪北韓，訪問當地民眾對於這位新任國際領導人的看法，發現北韓民眾對於美國的政治新聞只「略知一二」，民眾表示，當地媒體鮮少報導國際事務，多為北韓國內的新聞。<br />\n<br />\nCNN記者訪問了幾位北韓民眾，一位擔任研究員的男子表示，北韓的媒體很少報導國際新聞，民眾大多只關心自己國內的消息，不過，他們都知道，川普是「歐巴馬卸任以後的繼任總統」，他只想知道川普對於北韓的政策。<br />\n一名電腦工程師則表示，他對美國的各別事務不感興趣，只希望川普能與北韓建立友善關係。另一位擔任教師的受訪者也指出，他不在乎美國正由誰領導，他相信在金正恩的帶領下，北韓能在兩國的關係中爭取好的結果。<br />\n一對受訪的夫妻自信的指出：「我們更關心的是我們的日常生活，我們活得很好，在金正恩的領導下，一切都沒什麼問題」、「...我不覺得我們有因此受到什麼影響」。<br />\n美國網友看到北韓民眾對於美國事務的看法，自嘲：「這些北韓人跟很多美國人一樣，只關心自己國家的事。」也有表示，北韓民眾長久以來活在政府的限制底下，形同活在「黑暗」裡。幾位網友則說，他們也不在乎北韓民眾怎麼看待川普。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/2017/new/feb/21/images/bigPic/400_400/php7ERV2V.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2017%2Fnew%2Ffeb%2F21%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F400_400%2Fphp7ERV2V.jpeg&h=a643ac53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCNN記者訪問北韓民眾對川普的看法，結果顯示，北韓民眾對於美國政權只「略知一二」，對於北韓國內的消息比較關心。（圖擷自CNN）"},{"pid":"199e580afdfd9fa80c4ac1c1661d0c7dbc94b0b2","tid":129439,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T15:17:09.000Z","msg":"金正男死左點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a35bf30189260442c54c02188ca2abfe6c6d075","tid":129439,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T15:19:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金正男死左點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n北泡人:有死到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e539c02d5699fa90bf96b7520ab899237aac2a2","tid":129439,"uid":10509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T15:25:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金正男死左點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該會問邊個係金正男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9fa3a3d1756c7150dabd913c09ba414128908e7","tid":129439,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T15:29:53.000Z","msg":"(real) very fake news"},{"pid":"d050474425daa97ac69c108dcfecfda047ea7f16","tid":129439,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T15:51:49.000Z","msg":"飯都無得食仲有咩心機睇外國新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbabeb90bfe485388737d999dcd1a60918e8c93b","tid":129439,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T16:18:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}